data.description: Beautifully maintained condo w/ private entrance and 2 car garage. 3 BR, 2 1/2 bath. Eat in kitchen w/ portable island, and all appliances. Balcony off of kitchen suitable for a small grill. Hardwood first floor, carpet second floor. Ceiling fans in all bedrooms. All rooms professionally painted.Basement level provides separate laundry room and partial basement for storage. Sufficient closet space throughout. Close to I-90, and Bartlett Metra station. Pets negotiable. No smoking. Criminal background check required. Not approved for Section 8.
